{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_71","type":"agent_message","text":"# Implementation Response (Iteration 1)\n\n## Changes Made\n1. Hardened the claimed-task lifecycle in [daemon_loop.rs](/root/new-ralph-burning/ralph-burning-rewrite/src/contexts/automation_runtime/daemon_loop.rs) so failures after claim but before or around dispatch now fail the task, log the transition, release the lease, clear the task’s lease reference, and remove the worktree instead of exiting with orphaned daemon state.\n2. Updated [daemon.rs](/root/new-ralph-burning/ralph-burning-rewrite/src/cli/daemon.rs) so `daemon abort <task-id>` cleans up both `claimed` and `active` tasks: it marks the task aborted, gives an active daemon a short window to observe the persisted abort and cancel via the existing cancellation path, then falls back to releasing the lease and clearing the worktree/task lease reference itself if needed.\n3. Changed polling in [daemon_loop.rs](/root/new-ralph-burning/ralph-burning-rewrite/src/contexts/automation_runtime/daemon_loop.rs) to honor `poll_interval` after every cycle, and added CLI regressions in [tests/cli.rs](/root/new-ralph-burning/ralph-burning-rewrite/tests/cli.rs) for active-task abort cleanup and post-claim failure cleanup. Verified with `nix develop -c cargo test`.\n\n## Could Not Address\n- None\n\n## Pending Changes (Pre-Commit)\n- Uncommitted changes in [daemon_loop.rs](/root/new-ralph-burning/ralph-burning-rewrite/src/contexts/automation_runtime/daemon_loop.rs), [daemon.rs](/root/new-ralph-burning/ralph-burning-rewrite/src/cli/daemon.rs), [tests/cli.rs](/root/new-ralph-burning/ralph-burning-rewrite/tests/cli.rs), and [20260312231034-impl-response-III.md](/root/new-ralph-burning/ralph-burning-rewrite/20260312231034-impl-response-III.md).\n\n---"}}
{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_29","type":"todo_list","items":[{"text":"Patch daemon loop to fail-and-clean claimed tasks on any pre-dispatch error and honor poll cadence every cycle","completed":true},{"text":"Patch daemon abort to handle active-task cleanup via abort signalling plus bounded wait/fallback lease release","completed":true},{"text":"Add regression tests for active abort cleanup and post-claim failure cleanup, then run project verification and write review-response notes","completed":true}]}}
